{
  "stem": "7683.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And although some different experiences-- see, the Polish Jews experienced differently than the Dutch Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Polish Jews knew more what's going on, all the same situation as me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody believed it, but later you knew where you are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like when the Polish women went to hair-- cut hair, cut the hair, they were yelling.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They felt already what's going on, and they felt always very sad-- not sadly, but yelling and screaming and things like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Dutch women, they still believed it's just what they told them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They go to a camp working, and they cut the hair because the infection of-- they get lice or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So there was a different reaction by the not-- the Dutch Jews than the Polish Jews or the others.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, surely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The basic thing was not [? longer ?] sorting the clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to check all the clothes, all of this money in or food, because the people what were brought on transport brought with them-- they could take only what they could carry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because of that, everybody didn't know where he goes or she goes, so they took all the valuables and make it as small as possible.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they sew it in the clothes, like gold, all those things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then all of these things went through our hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we sabotaged.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We brought a whole lot to the fire where they'd burn the waste.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So with all the papers we do to just to sabotage that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you couldn't do too much because it was obvious, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So food [? was ?] [? it. ?] We were not allowed to use the food, take the food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you took it and you did it, they caught you, you got shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
